OVERVIEW: Comprehensive project repair command that fixes multiple corruption
types

USAGE: xcodeproj-cli repair-project [--project <project>] [--workspace <workspace>] [--verbose] [--dry-run] [--backup]

OPTIONS:
  -p, --project <project> Path to .xcodeproj file (default: looks for
                          *.xcodeproj in current directory)
  -w, --workspace <workspace>
                          Path to .xcworkspace file
  -V, --verbose           Enable verbose output with performance metrics
  --dry-run               Preview changes without saving
  --backup                Create backup before making changes
  --version               Show the version.
  -h, --help              Show help information.

